Paspor dianggap rusak karena lembab, padahal paspor masih bagus, tulisan terbaca & foto jelas. Jadi total utk perpanjangan harus bayar 1,2juta. Bingung mau ngadu kemana... Dikira semua warga orang kaya.

When I got there, it was stated that the passport was damaged, I had to make a new application for 350 & pay a fine of 500. The previous application was considered void. The passport was considered damaged due to moisture, even though the passport was still good, the writing was legible & the photo was clear. So the total for the extension had to pay 1.2 million. Confused about where to complain... Thought all citizens were rich.

The registration was very easy and we could determine the arrival date to the North Jakarta Immigration Office ourselves according to our wishes. The service of the North Jakarta Immigration Office officers was very good, friendly, fast and there were 8 counters so the queue was not too long. To pick up a finished passport, it only took 5 working days 👍

Review: Kritik: kolom input terlalu banyak, padahal sudah upload ktp Saran: 1) extract data dari image KTP saja. Mgkn bisa pakai OCR atau tesseract OCR. 2) bikin save data / auto save data walau belum selesai proses pengajuan. Biar ga perlu ulang input data dari awal lagi. 2) eror nya diperjelas. Terutama utk kendala saat login/register. Sy punya dokumen ttg evaluasi dan saran utk UX aplikasi ini. Apabila berminat, mgkn bisa saya berikan. Terima kasih banyak sblmnya telah membantu proses mengurus paspor
Translated_Review: Criticism: too many input columns, even though the ID card has been uploaded Suggestions: 1) extract data from the ID card image only. Maybe you can use OCR or tesseract OCR. 2) create a save data / auto save data even though the application process has not been completed. So that you don't need to re-input data from the beginning again. 2) clarify the error. Especially for problems when logging in / registering. I have a document regarding the evaluation and suggestions for the UX of this application. If you are interested, maybe I can provide it. Thank you very much in advance for helping the passport process

I was greeted by an officer with queue number 22, I asked the officer why there were already so many queues, it turned out that the arrival time range in the application did not apply, it was still on a first come first served basis. !! Then why was I asked to choose an arrival time, I arrived early in the morning and could only be served around 10 am because I had to queue. It's trivial but it has an impact on customer satisfaction.

Review: Disatu sisi sdh ada playanan dri imigrasi dgn mngeluarkan aplikasi utk pembuatan atw mmperpanjang Paspor, namun lagi2 pola pikir ptugas rata2 masih old mind. Gak tau apakah itu sistem dari pusat, kanwil atw daerah masing2. Kok hrs ada lah fotocopy2 segala.. Gak go green kali bah Pas pngambilan paspor lg, hrs diprin bukti pmbayaran Dalih praturan No. 4 diresi pngambilan paspor. Padahal isinya hny mnunjukkan bukti pmbayaran, bukannya di prin Kn sblum foto, si pmohon sdh mntrsfr uangnya Ahsudahlah

I don't know whether it's a system from the center, regional office or each region. Why do they have to have photocopies and everything? It's not go green. When picking up the passport again, proof of payment must be printed. The excuse is regulation No. 4 on the passport collection receipt. In fact, the content only shows proof of payment, not printed. Before the photo, the applicant has transferred the money. Oh well

Review: Over all app nya sudah bagus, hanya saja kode id billing kadang lama keluar dan expiry time pembayaran terkadang molor, walau sudah expired tapi form permohonan tidak langsung terhapus incase kalau ada perubahan data, harus nunggu lama lagi biar bisa buat permohonan baru. Translated_Review: Overall the app is good, it's just that the billing ID code sometimes takes a long time to come out and the payment expiry time is sometimes delayed, even though it has expired, the application form is not immediately deleted in case there is a change in data, you have to wait a long time to be able to make a new application. One more thing, if possible there is an additional notification feature when the passport can be picked up so that applicants can come at the right time

Advice for friends who want to make a passport via M Passport: *Before using the application, search for tutorials first via YouTube/internet *Find a place with a good internet connection *The email you have must be active, check it often, because there is a lot of information about our application via email *Check the immigration location in other areas/cities if it is fully booked Advice for M Passport: *Hopefully you can change the location for making a passport without having to input data from the beginning again

Review: Alhamdulillah pendaftaran dipermudah menggunakan Aplikasi ini. Dikutip Senin, 21 Februari 2022 Pukul 18.00 WIB “Ditjen Imigrasi telah menerbitkan kebijakan baru mengenai implementasi M-Paspor. Jika sebelumnya kuota permohonan paspor dibuka setiap hari Jumat Pukul 14.00 WIB untuk rentang waktu satu minggu kedepan, kini kuota permohonan paspor dibuka untuk satu bulan kedepan setiap kali pembaruan. Pengaturan kuota M-Paspor dilakukan pada setiap hari kerja di akhir bulan pukul 09.00 WIB.”
Translated_Review: Alhamdulillah, registration is made easier using this application. Quoted Monday, February 21, 2022 at 18.00 WIB "The Directorate General of Immigration has issued a new policy regarding the implementation of M-Passport. If previously the passport application quota was opened every Friday at 14.00 WIB for a period of one week ahead, now the passport application quota is opened for one month ahead for each renewal. The M-Passport quota arrangement is carried out every working day at the end of the month at 09.00 WIB."

Review: Trik membuat paspor Mandiri. 1. isi form jika hilang datanya berarti refresh lg dg isi ulang email & password (yg sama) data gk akan hilang. 2. Pilih jadwal kedatangan. Jika pilihan jadwal sdh penuh. Tunggu pembukaan jdwl baru di tgl akhir bln pkl 13.00. 3. Segera Pilih tgl kedatangan yg tdk sedang dipilih org lain (jd rebutan susah loading). Pilih tgl yg agak jauh & segra pilih. 4.pembayaran, lihat terlebih dahulu di google "cara bayar paspor online".
Translated_Review: Tricks to make an Independent passport. 1. Fill in the form if the data is lost, it means refreshing it again by refilling the email & password (the same) the data will not be lost. 2. Select the arrival schedule. If the schedule options are full. Wait for the opening of a new schedule at the end of the month at 13.00. 3. Immediately select an arrival date that is not being selected by others (so it's hard to load). Choose a date that is a bit far away & select immediately. 4. Payment, first see on Google "how to pay for a passport online".

Pngalaman saya di hari Rabu jam 21.30 alhamdulillah lancar jaya dari mengisi data2, pilih tanggal, sampai status pembayaran lunas. Salut buat pengembangnya. Mngkin saran utk pengembang aplikasi ini, agar menambah bandwith terutama saat siang banyak masyarakat yg akses shg tdk terjadi aplikasi nge-lag atau macet.
Translated_Review: In my opinion, this is a passport application that really helps the community. Tips for users of this application are to fill in data and upload documents at night. My experience on Wednesday at 21.30, thank God, everything went smoothly from filling in data, choosing a date, to the payment status being paid in full. Salute to the developer. Maybe a suggestion for the developer of this application is to increase bandwidth, especially during the day when many people access it so that the application does not lag or crash.

Tgl 30 dtg tch k imigrasi MPP BMS diminta tnda bkti klo udh byr bgtu bka aplikasi hrs login ulang mn lp pin nya.akhrnya ambil bkti di Gmail ft copy trs foto udh selesai ,dan aplikasi sampai sekarang g bsa bka.

Ehhh, I didn't know I was wrong, the passport model should be the regular one, not the electronic one because it wasn't available for the BMS area. Finally, I re-registered from the beginning and it went smoothly and I got it a week later. On the 30th, I went to the BMS MPP immigration and was asked to sign the proof. If you have paid, to open the application, you have to log in again, get the pin ID. Finally, I took the proof in Gmail, copied it, and took a photo and it was finished, and the application still can't be opened until now.

Review: Tips memakai app ini per pengalaman: - SELALU pakai huruf kapital, karena begitu ada huruf kecil, data KTP akan jadi salah terbaca. - JANGAN minta paspor elektronik bikarbonat karena minim stok. Kalau Anda minta paspor elektronik lalu tidak muncul kantor imigrasi dekat rumah, Anda harus menghapus profil yang sudah dibuat aka mengulang dari awal. - Ketika sampai ke minta jadwal wawancara ketika sudah benar dengan 2 tips di atas, klik "Ya, lanjut" berkali-kali sampai datang email. - Sabar ya
Translated_Review: Tips for using this app based on experience: - ALWAYS use capital letters, because if there are small letters, the KTP data will be misread. - DO NOT ask for a bicarbonate electronic passport because of low stock. If you ask for an electronic passport and the immigration office near your house does not appear, you must delete the profile that has been created or start over. - When you get to the interview schedule request when it is correct with the 2 tips above, click "Yes, continue" repeatedly until an email arrives. - Be patient

Kita perlu menghargai usaha pemerintah dalam mempermudah kita, menghilangkan birokrasi yang berbelit, potensi pungli dan calo (penyebab mental rusak penyelenggara negara) Hari ini saya coba lagi, app mungkin sudah di upgrade, server sudah di upgrade. Pengajuan lancar. Terimakasih.

We need to appreciate the government's efforts in making things easier for us, eliminating complicated bureaucracy, potential extortion and brokers (causes of damaged mental state administrators) Today I tried again, the app may have been upgraded, the server has been upgraded. Submission went smoothly. Thank you.

Review: Konsep apk bagus. Dulu cuma antrian (meski ga nyambung update sama m-paspor), sekarang udah termasuk bayar PNBP paspornya. Jadi "penerimaan negara semakin tinggi", soalnya kalo kita batal/terlewat/ada kesalahan data, harus daftar ulang, artinya BAYAR LAGI, yg awal HANGUS. Mantap. Upload data pun terasa sia-sia karena di Imigrasi Depok (Detos) maupun Imigrasi Jakarta Timur, tetap meminta "FOTOKOPI" persyaratan. Gunanya upload foto paspor, ktp dll buat apa dong kalo tetep minta fotokopi?! HERAN!!
Translated_Review: The concept of the app is good. Previously it was just a queue (although it was not connected to the update with m-passport), now it includes paying the PNBP for the passport. So "state revenue is getting higher", because if we cancel/miss/there is a data error, we have to re-register, which means PAYING AGAIN, the initial one is FORFEITED. Great. Uploading data also feels useless because at Depok Immigration (Detos) and East Jakarta Immigration, they still ask for "PHOTOCOPY" of the requirements. What's the point of uploading passport photos, ID cards, etc. if they still ask for photocopies?! AMAZING!!

Review: To the point, aplikasi ini cukup lelet bahkan di ponsel dengan spek gahar sekalipun, Redmi Note 10 Pro misalnya. Durasi loading, navigasi antarmenu, entah kenapa tiap bagiannya terasa lambat. Untuk UI, sudah bagus dan konsisten. Alangkah baik jika ada fitur lacak status permohonan paspor, bukan manual via WhatsApp—agar aplikasi bisa lebih berguna. Kemudian, opsi pembayaran seharusnya ditampilkan lebih mudah dan jelas, bukan hanya menampilkan kode billing tanpa ada petunjuk pembayaran yang jelas.
Translated_Review: To the point, this application is quite slow even on phones with powerful specs, such as the Redmi Note 10 Pro. Loading duration, navigation between menus, for some reason each part feels slow. For the UI, it is good and consistent. It would be nice if there was a feature to track the status of a passport application, not manually via WhatsApp—so that the application can be more useful. Then, the payment options should be displayed more easily and clearly, not just displaying a billing code without any clear payment instructions.
